---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
  { name: 'Service Providers', url: '/for-providers' },
  { name: 'Boarding Facilities', url: '/for-providers/boarding-facilities' }
];
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Boarding Facilities on BreederHQ Marketplace"
  description="List your dog kennel, cat boarding cattery, exotic boarding, equine boarding, livestock boarding, or in-home boarding service on the BreederHQ Marketplace. $5/month, no commissions."
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
>
<main>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-green-50 to-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🏠</div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-6">Boarding Facilities</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Dog kennels, cat boarding catteries, exotic boarding, equine boarding, livestock boarding, and in-home boarding &mdash;
        owners are searching the BreederHQ Marketplace for trusted boarding for every species.
      </p>
      <a href="https://accounts.breederhq.com/register?intent=provider_marketplace&category=boarding_facility&returnTo=/services/facilities/boarding/new" class="bg-green-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-green-600">
        List Your Boarding Facility
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">What you can list</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Companion Animal Boarding</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Dog kennels with indoor or indoor/outdoor runs</li>
            <li>Cat boarding catteries with individual rooms</li>
            <li>Exotic boarding for reptiles, birds, and small mammals</li>
            <li>In-home boarding (your home, their home)</li>
            <li>Group play vs individual housing options</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Large-Animal Boarding</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Equine boarding stalls (short and long term)</li>
            <li>Livestock boarding for cattle, goats, sheep</li>
            <li>Pasture board with turnout</li>
            <li>Climate-controlled barns</li>
            <li>Quarantine accommodation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-stone-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Why it works for boarding facilities</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📅</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Holiday and travel demand</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Owners book months ahead for major holidays. A listing that surfaces in early planning wins the holiday season.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🩺</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Show your standards up front</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Vaccination requirements, emergency vet relationships, medication administration, and senior care all surface in your listing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📷</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Build trust with photos</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Owners want to see runs, suites, and outdoor space before they leave their animal. Photo-rich listings convert better.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Your listing includes</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-green-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Subtype, species supported, housing type, capacity</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-green-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Indoor and outdoor runs, climate control, individual vs group</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-green-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Webcams, daily reports, photo updates</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-green-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Medication administration, senior care, special-needs care</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-green-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Check-in / check-out windows, min and max stay</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-green-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Vaccination requirements, waivers, emergency vet relationship</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-6 text-center">
        Boarding facilities use a contact-to-book workflow: owners send an inquiry, you confirm dates and arrange payment directly.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-900 to-green-800">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white"><span class="line-through opacity-60 text-2xl">$5/mo</span> Free during early access</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-green-200 mb-3">No commissions. No per-night platform fees. Cancel anytime.</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-green-200 mb-8">Capture holiday and travel demand from owners actively searching boarding in your area.</p>
      <a href="https://accounts.breederhq.com/register?intent=provider_marketplace&category=boarding_facility&returnTo=/services/facilities/boarding/new" class="bg-white text-green-800 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-green-50">
        List Your Boarding Facility
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
